c: 6
v: 12
t: "Ask them, \"To whom belongs everything in the heavens and on earth?\" Say, \"To Allah!\" He has mandated mercy upon Himself. He would most certainly (bring you back to life and) gather all of you together on the day of Resurrection. There is no doubt about it! Those who have incurred a severe loss, and have ruined themselves, are the ones who refuse to believe"